    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, a high-revving masterpiece equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis has been enhanced with proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, addressing the primary technical concerns of this platform. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative, paired with a factory-spec multi-link rear suspension that maintains the car's legendary handling balance. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical components are robust, offering a sharp throttle response and the unmistakable metallic rasp of the factory-tuned exhaust. A turn-key specimen for the purist seeking an analog performance experience.",
