    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily practicality. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of any tears or significant staining, while the dashboard and trim pieces remain vibrant and crack-free. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and ready for the open road. It has been treated to a rigorous schedule of synthetic oil changes and recently underwent a comprehensive inspection, resulting in fresh brake pads and a new set of high-performance all-season tires. The engine idles smoothly and the transmission shifts with crisp precision, offering a driving experience that feels tight and well-sorted. Included with the sale are a complete set of service records and a clean title, ensuring a transparent and confident purchase for the next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
