      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system, ensuring peak variable valve timing performance. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced to maintain structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, preserving the communicative steering and neutral handling balance this chassis is famous for. A driver-spec machine that prioritizes mechanical health and performance over garage-queen status.",
